sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as Classes List Page
    participant LW as Livewire Component
    participant DB as Database

    User->>UI: Open classes page
    UI->>LW: Initial request
    LW->>DB: Query classes (+ institute, campus, programme, students_count)
    DB-->>LW: Paginated result set
    LW-->>UI: Render table, filters, pagination

    User->>UI: Search/filter/sort/paginate
    UI->>LW: Update bound properties
    LW->>DB: Re-query with conditions
    DB-->>LW: Updated paginated result
    LW-->>UI: Re-render table

    User->>UI: Delete class
    UI->>LW: deleteClass(id)
    LW->>DB: Delete class row
    alt Success
        DB-->>LW: Deleted
        LW-->>UI: Success toast + refresh
    else In use
        DB-->>LW: QueryException
        LW-->>UI: Error toast
    end
